{
  "stem": "21582.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, what you heard during the bombing was from the Polish government.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, their reports reflected propaganda.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and, and they kind of kept you informed about what was going on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you had quite a few Volksdeutsche, which is Poles who-- whose ancestors were Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they identified-- much more, or many-- identified with-- they saw themselves as Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they were educated in Polish schools.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they spoke the language.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were Polish citizens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took over the radio.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We-- well, we didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one night, we hear that broadcast on the radio.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was a broadcast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We did not hear it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But apparently enough people did hear the broadcasting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, in the middle of the night, the gate was rattling.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my aunt and my uncle came pleading with my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They said, you must-- you must leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because-- and then we turned on the radio.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then we heard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the-- it got-- they-- the voice that came through on the radio identified themselves as Poles and said that the President [NON-ENGLISH]-- he was saying, in his name, all Polish young-- all Polish men lay down your, your guns and move towards Russia.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Run away.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because when the Germans come and every single man is, is killed-- they just slaughter indiscriminately.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, they did that to cause panic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Well, my father left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we just felt so devastated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My mother-- and we were just so devastated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I recall we just-- we couldn't-- my mother-- we could not bear staying home and be reminded of my father and that his presence wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So we went to that same aunt, all cousins and, and, and, and aunts-- we-- and my mother, my sister, and I.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
